<objectives component="profesor">
  <ul>
    <li>[+++++++++++++++]</li>
    <li>Count to answer “how many” questions about images presented in lines, arrays, circles, on fingers, and on 5-frames.</li>
    <li>Match written numbers and groups of images.</li>
